{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"30084-baagadnara-dukru","title":"अवखळ डुकरू","description":"मिनी सिंग या कुंभाराची ललिता नावाची लाडकी पाळीव डुकरीण आहे. हे अवखळ डुकरू नेहमी काहीतरी गडबड करून ठेवतं. एके दिवशी मिनीनं बनवलेली सगळी मातीची सुंदर भांडी तुटलेली-फुटलेली दिसतात. ती सारी ललितानेच फोडली आहेत, असं त्याला वाटतं. पण खरंच तसं होतं का? वाचू या गोष्टीत. आणि हो, ही ललिता नावाची डुकरीण पुणे इथं खरोखरच एका कुंभाराकडे राहते बरं का. ","language":"Marathi","langCode":"mr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jui Kulkarni"],"illustrators":["Priya Kuriyan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/30084-baagadnara-dukru"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/167262/size3/ca6c5111d8ce48f2a627f7fdece3807e.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/167262/size6/ca6c5111d8ce48f2a627f7fdece3807e.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/30084/audios/story/30084-baagadnara-dukru.mp3","cues":[[1,0,2.56],[2,2.56,3.4],[3,3.4,3.76],[4,3.76,4.04],[5,4.04,5.16],[6,5.16,6.6],[7,6.6,7.28],[8,7.28,8.88],[9,8.88,9.24],[10,9.24,9.96],[11,9.96,10.8],[12,10.8,11.36],[13,11.36,11.96],[14,11.96,13.84],[15,13.84,14.56],[16,14.56,15.36],[17,15.36,16.4],[18,16.4,16.84],[19,16.84,19.32],[20,19.32,22.28],[21,22.28,23.72],[22,23.72,24.96],[23,24.96,25.88],[24,25.88,26.88],[25,26.88,27.72],[26,27.72,28.68],[27,28.68,29.56],[28,29.56,30.16],[29,30.16,31.2],[30,31.2,31.76],[31,31.76,33.52],[32,33.52,35.44],[33,35.44,36.44],[34,36.44,37.84],[35,37.84,39.24],[36,39.24,39.96],[37,39.96,41.28],[38,41.28,41.96],[39,41.96,42.44],[40,42.44,44.44],[41,44.44,45.8],[42,45.8,49.12],[43,49.12,50.04],[44,50.04,50.92],[45,50.92,51.92],[46,